43 (2) The State Board of Education shall be authorized to establish reporting requirements
44 on the public schools and local school systems participating in the grant program.
45 (d) The Department of Education shall develop and publish on its public website an
46 application process and seek applications from public schools and local school systems for
47 the grant program no later than September 1, 2025. Reserved."
48 SECTION 3.
49 All laws and parts of laws in conflict with this Act are repealed.
